---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- Problem Section -->
<section
  id="problem"
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 border-t border-gray-800 relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-16">
      What's important to you?
    </h2>
    <div
      class="prose prose-lg sm:prose-xl prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12"
    >
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
        You are already infinitely rich—like an oil-rich country with unknown
        reserves of wisdom and experience you've accumulated but haven't yet
        articulated. Discovery and mining for these riches is integral to our
        process. You don't need to arrive with a specific conundrum or be in
        crisis.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">What drives your choices?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            The values and principles that have been growing in you, shaping how
            you respond to what matters most
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
            What makes life meaningful?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            The sources of importance that call forth more of yourself—your
            natural response to what you treasure
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-400 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Who are you becoming?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            The growth trajectory you're already on—where you've come from and
            what you're growing toward
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-400 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">How do you want to live?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            The philosophy of living that's emerging from your experience,
            waiting to be heard and articulated
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#solution" text="How conversation helps" />
  </div>
</section>
